        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2977168223" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9051499657544303878">This was <i>amazing</i>. I had initially planned on just reading the script, but when I picked it up I spontaneously looked on YouTube if there was a recording of a performance and oh yes, there was. It was incredible. Funny, tragic, surrealist and all-to-real. All the stars. A serious contender for my favorite play of all time.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


