<div id="review_3487526732" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3487526732" />
    <a title="Anna Schaeffer" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/113327081-anna-schaeffer"><img alt="Anna Schaeffer" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1587043991p2/113327081.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3487526732?book_show_action=true">Aug 09, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Anna Schaeffer" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Anna Schaeffer" href="/user/show/113327081-anna-schaeffer">Anna Schaeffer</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3487526732" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2732866881031588490">Part 1 of Angels in America is heavy on dark humor and light on predictability. Each character escapes two-dimensionality and presents the reader/audience with plenty to think on. The themes are broad: sexuality and politics, global migration, religiosity, and US democracy. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

